		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="Re:Anonymous payments by SanityInAnarchy" data-url="http://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2244306&cid=36462806" data-title="Re:Anonymous payments">facebook</a>
		<a class="janrain l" href="#" data-provider="linkedin" data-message="Re:Anonymous payments by SanityInAnarchy" data-url="http://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2244306&cid=36462806" data-title="Re:Anonymous payments">linkedin</a>
		<a class="g" href="http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2244306%26cid=36462806" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href,'', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;"><img src="//www.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png" alt="Share on Google+"/></a>
