		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="Still an ad.  Again and again. by Jiro" data-url="http://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2244306&cid=36463368" data-title="Still an ad.  Again and again.">facebook</a>
