			<h4><a id="comment_link_36461894" name="comment_link_36461894" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2244306&amp;cid=36461894" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(36461894)" >Re:What the hell is a bitcoin?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_36461894" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 36461894); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Thud457">Thud457</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Thud457">(234763)</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
